text: Paul Egloff (born 15 October 1959) is a Swiss ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1980 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Switzerland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1980 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
